This product is a clean-room implementation of public standards: RFC 5545 (iCalendar
recurrence), RFC 8536 (TZif), and the public IANA time zone database.

It depends on:
  - python-dateutil (Apache-2.0 / BSD-3-Clause) — an independent RFC 5545 implementation.
  - tzdata (Apache-2.0) — the public IANA time zone database packaged for Python.

